Brian Molefe is Appointed as Chief Executive of South Africa's Transnet

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-02-16T13:06:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/brian-molefe-is-appointed-as-chief-executive-of-south-africa-s-transnet.html
Brian Molefe, the former head of  South Africa ’s Public Investment Corp., has been appointed as
Chief Executive Officer of Transnet Ltd, the state-owned rail
and ports company, Malusi Gigaba, the country’s public
enterprises minister, said in  Cape Town  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
